      "how_to_add": "Panel A → 导入参保信息 → 支持标准参保 JSON/CSV 格式"
    },
    {
      "table": "insurance_policy_rules",
      "description": "各统筹区医保政策规则（起付线、报销比例、封顶线、甲乙丙分类规则）",
      "used_by_domains": ["outpatient","inpatient","pharmacy","cross-region","drg","maternity","catastrophic","medical-assistance","tcm"],
      "how_to_add": "Panel A → 导入政策规则库 → 支持省/市级规则 JSON"
